Ôªø<html metal:use-macro="here/@@standard_macros/master">
  <head>
    <title metal:fill-slot="title" tal:content="string:Tour - ${view/area/Title} on ${view/portal_title}" />
  </head>
  <body>

    <div metal:fill-slot="content">

      <div id="oc-content-main">
        <div class="oc-headingBlock">
          <h1>Welcome to <span tal:replace="string:${view/portal_title}" />!</h1>
          <p class="oc-headingContext">We hope you will use this website to plan events, start projects, and improve your communities. Now you can&hellip;</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="oc-getstarted">
          <h2><a tal:attributes="href string:${context/absolute_url}/profile-edit">Complete your profile</a></h2>
          <p>Let other <span tal:replace="string:${view/portal_title}" /> members know who you are and what you're interested in. The more information you provide, the more contacts you'll make.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="oc-getstarted">
          <h2><a tal:attributes="href string:${view/portal_url}/projects">Join a project and help it succeed</a></h2>
          <p>Found something you're interested in? Want to volunteer an hour of your time? Join a project and help someone's vision become a reality.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="oc-getstarted">
          <h2><a tal:attributes="href string:${view/portal_url}/projects/create">Start your own project</a></h2>
          <p>Is there something you'd like to do? Install bike parking? Create a community garden? Throw a block party? Start your own project and use our toolkit to stay organized.</p>
        </div>
      </div><!-- end #oc-content-main -->

      <div id="oc-content-sidebar">
        <div class="ox-boxy" tal:define="invitations view/invitations"
              tal:condition="invitations">
          <h2>You have been invited to:</h2>
          <ul class="oc-invite-list">
            <form name="invitation-form" action="account">
              <tal:for repeat="projinfo invitations">
                <li class="oc-invite oc-boxy oc-clearAfter"
                    tal:define="proj_id projinfo/proj_id"
                    tal:attributes="id string:${proj_id}_invitation"> 
                  <p class="oc-invite-content">
                    <a href="" tal:attributes="href string:${view/portal_url}/projects/${proj_id}" tal:content="projinfo/title">Animal Campaign</a> 
                    has invited you to become a member
                  </p>
                  <ul class="oc-actions oc-invite-actions oc-actionClose"
                      tal:define="url request/ACTUAL_URL">
                    <li tal:repeat="action view/invitation_actions">
                      <a tal:attributes="href string:${url}?task|${proj_id}|${action}Invitation=${action};
                       class string:oc-actionLink oc-js-actionLink oc-choose${action}"
                   tal:content="action"
                   />
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                </li>
              </tal:for>
            </form>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="oc-boxy" tal:define="projects view/project_brains"
              tal:condition="projects">
          <h2>Projects you belong to:</h2>
          <ul class="oc-directory-list oc-bigText oc-clearAfter">
            <li class="oc-clearAfter" tal:repeat="project projects" style="width: 96%;">
              <div class="oc-project-logo">
                <a tal:attributes="href project/getURL">
                  <img src="++resource++img/default-projlogo-thumb.gif" tal:attributes="alt project/Title" />
                </a>
              </div>
              <div class="oc-directory-content">
                <a tal:attributes="href project/getURL" tal:content="project/Title" />
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div><!-- end #oc-content-sidebar -->

  </div><!-- content-fill-slot -->
  </body>
</html>

